#: ../../source/janim/render/framebuffer.rst:2
msgid "framebuffer"
msgstr "framebuffer"

#: janim.render.framebuffer.qt_framebuffer_patch:1 of
msgid "自动在 with 前获取 GL 对象，在 with 后重设 GL 对象（如果是 Qt 的 Framebuffer），以保证与 Qt 的兼容"
msgstr ""
"Automatically obtains the GL object before ``with`` and resets it after ``with`` (if it is a Qt Framebuffer), to ensure "
"compatibility with Qt"

#: janim.render.framebuffer.FrameBuffer.unpremultiply:1 of
msgid "将当前 FBO 的 PMA 内容通过 GPU pass 转为 straight alpha，结果写回自身"
msgstr "Convert the current FBO's PMA content to straight alpha via GPU pass; write the result back"
